228
00:24:23,735 --> 00:24:27,617
[SPEAKER_05]: Like, are the parents required to acknowledge the filing

229
00:24:28,303 --> 00:24:28,823
[SPEAKER_05]: in some way?

230
00:24:32,906 --> 00:24:50,317
[SPEAKER_03]: I was going to say, depending on the age of the child and at the high school where the kids are much older, but if it were to be in the younger grades, we definitely would have to have parent involvement and consent for them to know what was going on.

