00:26:29,757 --> 00:26:31,278
[SPEAKER_00]: I just want to say exactly what Nick said.

243
00:26:31,298 --> 00:26:39,241
[SPEAKER_00]: And so in that, and we always keep a log of when we contact families as well, so that nobody can turn around and say, well, we were never informed.

244
00:26:39,361 --> 00:26:41,742
[SPEAKER_00]: And sometimes investigations do take a long time.

245
00:26:42,182 --> 00:26:47,524
[SPEAKER_00]: But what we like to do is say, we're still working on it, just so you know, because sometimes witnesses are absent.

246
