[SPEAKER_00]: Sometimes they're absent for longer periods of time than we'd want.

247
00:26:50,845 --> 00:26:57,287
[SPEAKER_00]: And so we just kind of keep a running log of the communication home, but always try to keep everybody in the loop, because sometimes they do take a while.

248
00:26:57,447 --> 00:27:00,888
