486
00:52:54,093 --> 00:53:15,368
[SPEAKER_02]: And I'll also note just, if I may, to be effective in this regard, schools have really found success in preventing bullying just through broader efforts, including the topics like social-emotional learning and school climate-based programming, and making sure that we're infusing these, not just through health or wellness class, but across all disciplines.

487
00:53:15,929 --> 00:53:20,132
