488
00:53:20,904 --> 00:53:37,432
[SPEAKER_02]: And I think we need to be thoughtful in that, because that's where the research is saying that you're going to have some really effective anti-bullying type of campaigns if we're weaving it and infusing it in everything that we do in all of our practices across our schools, K through 12.

